message: Hello Bob, I'm pleased to offer you my exclusive product for $5000000. I believe this product represents outstanding value and quality, and I'm confident it will meet your high expectations. If you agree with this price, please let me know. Otherwise, feel free to propose a counteroffer. Just so you know, I do have another interested buyer willing to pay $1000000, so I'm looking for a deal that truly reflects the premium nature of this product.
Thank you for your offer, Alice. However, $5000000 is beyond my budget. I am willing to offer $600000 for your product, considering its value to me. Please let me know if this works for you.
